input_str: ORLANDO, Fla. (July 17, 2016) – Orlando City SC captain Kaká and striker Cyle Larin have been named to the 2016 AT&T Major League Soccer (MLS) All-Star Game, joining the league’s best talents to face English Premier League side Arsenal FC on Thursday, July 28 at Avaya Stadium in San Jose, Calif. The match will be broadcast live at 7:30 p.m. ET on ESPN
